---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Learn how SecureLiving.com collects, uses, and protects your information. We're committed to your privacy and transparent about our data practices.">
  <div class="container legal-page">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> September 1, 2025</p>

    <p>At SecureLiving.com, your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and your rights regarding that information.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We do not collect personally identifiable information (such as names, addresses, or emails) when you browse our site. However, we may automatically collect certain information about your visit through Google Analytics, including:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>The pages you visit on our site</li>
      <li>How long you spend on each page</li>
      <li>General information about your device, browser, and location (e.g., city or region, not exact address)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>This data is collected anonymously and cannot be used to personally identify you.</p>

    <h2>How We Use This Information</h2>
    <p>We use Google Analytics data to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Understand how visitors use our site</li>
      <li>Improve the content and structure of our website</li>
      <li>Monitor overall traffic and site performance</li>
    </ul>
    <p>This information is used only in aggregate and is not linked to individual users.</p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We use Google Analytics, a service provided by Google, Inc., to analyze site usage. Google may use cookies or similar technologies to collect data about your browsing behavior.</p>
    <p>You can learn more about how Google uses your data here: <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Privacy & Terms</a>.</p>
    <p>If you wish, you can opt out of Google Analytics tracking by installing the browser add-on available here: <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics Opt-out</a>.</p>

    <h2>Your Privacy Choices</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Control or delete cookies through your browser settings</li>
      <li>Opt out of Google Analytics tracking using the tools linked above</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or services. Updates will be posted on this page with a new effective date.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at:<br />
    <a href="mailto:support@secureliving.com">support@secureliving.com</a></p>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
